jection of Andy Tsang's nomination to United Nations positions (RE-PETITION) <br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=785dd031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition</a>"},{"pid":"796d238968fde96f5629866b50536203d586dc9c","tid":1561414,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:04:39.000Z","msg":"嘩屌p牌完全無人理<br />\nBook mark咗聽朝人多幫你推"},{"pid":"a8d2e2c23e392f61ef0372c1bcc386bf06ea3921","tid":1561414,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:14:33.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"83c1db0f1e3df262ec7db9e42fb6954abbaad37d","tid":1561414,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:17:50.000Z","msg":"人類要贏，共產黨就要輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">九月十五，港島見！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wewHJNK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwewHJNK.jpg&h=1ea6c586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88ee6794d7c07bb5ef81c4a31dfe43be3b258df5","tid":1561414,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:21:45.000Z","msg":"同意，幫推！"},{"pid":"8a3306f79447110fa104185d00d5cea16e5198c8","tid":1561414,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T20:07:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0a8009c